title: Top 30 Country May 13, 2014
description:
Thomas Rhett hits number one with Get Me Some Of That and we have 2 new songs debuting this week on the Chart including a duet from Tim McGraw & Faith Hill along with the new song from Chase Rice.  Here are the Top 30 U.S. Country singles according to Mediabase for the week of May 13, 2014 at 320 CBR Stereo.
